            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2 group-hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors">Building Load Forecasting with LSTM-T-KAN</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-4 text-sm leading-relaxed">
              Proposed LSTM-T-KAN, a dual-branch framework that combines LSTM for temporal modeling with Kolmogorov-Arnold Networks for nonlinear correction, using multi-source features (temporal, environmental, statistical and time-frequency) to achieve accurate and interpretable multiscale building load forecasting on real-world office building data.
            </p>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-500 mb-4">
